Creating A Todo List

* Create useStates to store the task to be added and the array of tasks.
* Add an onChange event to thr input.
* Add an onClick to the button.
* Write a fumction to handle the button click event.
* Add each task to the array of tasks after the button is clicked.
* Map throuh the tasks and display them on the browser.

